{"tid":2142111,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"共匪：《基本法》第一章第一條列明港中一體 永續基本法是個好東西","createTime":"2020-08-06T07:39:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T07:57:11.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5228b3ce1316f79e955bc42b74b824dab5cb1c43","tid":2142111,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T07:39:35.000Z","msg":"董建華：時間會證明港區國安法不影響司法獨立<br />\n<br />\n全國政協副主席董建華表示，《港區國安法》有效防止外國反華勢力，利用香港作為分裂祖國的基地，針對的是極少數危害國家安全的犯罪份子，絕對不會影響廣大市民享有的合法權利和自由，絕對不會影響香港的獨立司法權和終審權，相信時間會證明一切。<br />\n<br />\n董建華在團結香港基金的講座致辭時表示，今年是《基本法》頒布30周年，希望大家正確認識《基本法》的精神，「一國」是「兩制」的前提，國家的《憲法》是《基本法》的根源，行政主導是香港成功的基石，循序漸進是政治發展的原則，他希望大家共同維護特區憲制基礎，推動一國兩制行穩致遠。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2350909\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2350909&d=il%2BrReVPph3FBkDtfLAFOkPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=2fb6234a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2350909</a>"},{"pid":"272a730d45a452ea3405c769f9182b69c40a124c","tid":2142111,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T07:40:49.000Z","msg":"老懵董你幾時賠返條命畀老人家呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2744c5230739e096b34df6e01be366bc969ce587","tid":2142111,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T07:41:59.000Z","msg":"熱狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2c802a4da0717157283ba425776f9237808b216","tid":2142111,"uid":143499,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T07:43:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0acedb4abe35ab9895070086a85b2632659e52a1","tid":2142111,"uid":254450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T07:57:11.000Z","msg":"敗晒老豆副身家嘅二世祖有咩資格教人做嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.g